00:02:35.100 --> 00:02:37.290
So this guy is going
to see a and b.

00:02:37.290 --> 00:02:40.470
This guy right here is going to
see the foreheads c and a.

00:02:40.470 --> 00:02:42.520
And then this guy's going
to see these two

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:44.220
